SELECT
  $__timeGroup("Timestamp"::timestamp, $__interval) AS time,
  avg("Solar_Panel_Current_A_01") AS sp_01,
  avg("Solar_Panel_Current_A_02") AS sp_02,
  avg("Solar_Panel_Current_A_03") AS sp_03,
  avg("Solar_Panel_Current_A_04") AS sp_04,
  avg("Solar_Panel_Current_A_05") AS sp_05,
  avg("Solar_Panel_Current_A_06") AS sp_06,
  avg("Solar_Panel_Current_A_07") AS sp_07,
  avg("Solar_Panel_Current_A_08") AS sp_08,
  avg("Solar_Panel_Current_A_09") AS sp_09
FROM
  "HEALTH_EPS"
WHERE
  $__timeFilter("Timestamp"::timestamp)
GROUP BY
  time
ORDER BY
  time
